Item.Title: Lucy Goes to the Hospital (Broadcast Version)
Welcome Little Ricky
Item.Description: The I Love Lucy broadcast of January 19, 1953, the day on which both "Little Ricky" Ricardo and Desi Arnaz, Jr., were born, did not end with the usual closing commercial. Rather, Philip Morris filled the time with a heartfelt message commemorating the birth of the Ricardo infant and congratulating his TV parents.

Item.Title: Heart Fund PSA
Item.Description: The March 23, 1953, repeat of "The Seance" concluded with a special Public Service Announcement for the Heart Fund, featuring Lucy and Desi.
